name: Commission Report
query:
SELECT
    t1.name AS Id,
    t1.invoice AS Invoice,
    t1.invoice_status AS 'Invoice Status',
    t1.commission_status AS 'Commission Status',
    t1.amount AS Amount,
    t1.percentage AS Percentage,
    (t1.amount / (t1.percentage / 100)) AS 'Grand Total'
FROM
    `tabCommission Transaction` t1
